sequenceDiagram
    participant Script as main_pipeline
    participant Chroma as ChromaDB
    participant Pipeline as RAGPipeline
    participant SP as ServicePredictor
    participant QR as LlamaQueryRewriter
    participant Ollama as Ollama API
    participant HR as HybridRetriever
    participant RR as Reranker

    Script->>Chroma: PersistentClient() + get_collection("aws_docs")
    Script->>Pipeline: __init__(collection)
    Pipeline->>SP: __init__()
    Pipeline->>QR: __init__(n_queries=2)
    Pipeline->>RR: __init__() — loads CrossEncoder model
    Pipeline->>HR: __init__(collection)
    Pipeline->>HR: build_bm25_index()
    HR->>Chroma: collection.get(include=["documents"])
    Chroma-->>HR: all documents
    HR-->>Pipeline: BM25 index ready

    Script->>Pipeline: query(q)

    Pipeline->>SP: predict(query, top_k=2)
    Note over SP: cosine similarity vs service embeddings
    SP-->>Pipeline: [(service, score), ...]

    Pipeline->>QR: rewrite(query)
    QR->>Ollama: POST /api/generate — llama3
    Ollama-->>QR: 2 alternative query formulations
    QR-->>Pipeline: rewritten_queries[]

    loop for each rewritten query
        Pipeline->>HR: hybrid_search(q, alpha=0.5, top_k=20, service_filter)
        HR->>Chroma: collection.query(query_texts, where={service})
        Chroma-->>HR: vector search results + distances
        Note over HR: BM25 scores computed in-memory
        Note over HR: hybrid = 0.5 * vec_score + 0.5 * bm25_score
        HR-->>Pipeline: scored candidates[]
    end

    Note over Pipeline: union + deduplicate by text

    Pipeline->>RR: rerank(original_query, candidates, top_k=5)
    Note over RR: CrossEncoder scores each (query, doc) pair
    RR-->>Pipeline: top-5 results with rerank_score

    Pipeline-->>Script: results[{text, vector_score, bm25_score, hybrid_score, rerank_score}]
    Script->>Script: confidence_label(scores[0], scores[1])
    Script->>Script: print query + confidence
